:{{see|Wissen}}

----

==German==
===Etymology===
Middle High German ''wizzen'', originally *''witten''
===Verb===
'''wissen''' (''third-person singular simple present'' '''[[weiß]]''', ''[[preterite]]'' '''[[wusste]]''', ''[[past participle]]'' '''[[gewusst]]''', ''auxiliary verb in composite tenses'' '''[[haben]]''')

# to [[know]] (in general)
#:''Ich weiß, wo du bist''
#::I know where you are

